<para id="fs-id1164565770989">When are two bodies in thermal equilibrium?</para>
<list id="fs-id1164567294421" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>When they are in thermal contact and are at different pressures</item>
<item>When they are not in thermal contact but are at the same pressure</item>
<item>When they are not in thermal contact but are at different temperatures</item>
<item>When they are in thermal contact and are at the same temperature</item>
</list>
</problem>
